title: Finding Dracula In Avengers #15
body:
Finding Dracula In Avengers #15

[*Mild Spoilers Ahead!]

The Shadow Colonel and his Hellhound, the Sarge, are loose in Avengers Mountain. They’ve corrupted the Ghost Rider somehow, and this allows them to make their escape with the Ghost Rider added to their ranks. Meanwhile, Iron Man has snuck into the Russian prison that is holding Dracula. The old vampire lord appears to be spent, as he is now emaciated and physically weak.…

You’re the same people who go on Rotten Tomatoes and talk shit about the movie without even having seen it because you’re pissed Brie is an outspoken feminist.
